哈雷電單車吸引了一群忠實的品牌愛好者<ref>{{cite web |title=Harley-Davidson's 100th anniversary - the sound of a legend |author=Richard Pierson and Alexander Bozmoski |work=Sound and Vibration |url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qa4075/is_200303/ai_n9223788 |accessdate=2007-12-13 |date=March 2003 |archive-date=2011-06-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110624040731/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_qa4075/is_200303/ai_n9223788/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。哈雷·戴維森商標的授權收入約佔了該公司營業額的5%（2004年時為4,100萬美元）<ref>{{cite book | title = The Standard & Poor's 500 Guide | publisher = McGraw-Hill Professional | author = Standard & Poor's | id = ISBN 978-0-07-146823-7 | accessdate = 2007-12-22}}</ref> 。在2003年，[[Buell_Motorcycle_Company|Buell Motorcycle Company]]，成為哈雷·戴維森全資持有的子公司<ref>{{cite web | title = Buell Motorcycle Co. - Two Wheel Innovation | publisher = US Industry Today | url = http://www.usitoday.com/article_view.asp?ArticleID=1485 | accessdate = 2007-12-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080306054727/http://www.usitoday.com/article_view.asp?ArticleID=1485 | archivedate = 2008-03-06 }}</ref>，而就在同一年哈雷·戴維森也迎接創立的一百週年。在2008年8月，哈雷·戴維森買下義大利摩托車製造商[[MV_Agusta|MV Agusta]]<ref>{{cite web |title=Harley-Davidson Completes Acquisition of MV Agusta |publisher=Motorcycle Daily.com |url=http://www.motorcycledaily.com/080808pressrelease1.htm |accessdate=2008-09-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090503053454/http://www.motorcycledaily.com/080808pressrelease1.htm |archivedate=2009-05-03 }}</ref>。哈雷·戴維森還是美國[[警察|警用]]摩托車的主要供應商<ref name="On Patrol">{{cite web |title=On Patrol |work=2005 Harley-Davidson Police Motorcycles |url=http://www.mapc.org/services/GBPC/Harley/On%20Patrol%202005%20Harley-Davidson%20Police%20Motorcycles%20Catalog.pdf |format=PDF |accessdate=2007-06-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070927190348/http://www.mapc.org/services/GBPC/Harley/On%20Patrol%202005%20Harley-Davidson%20Police%20Motorcycles%20Catalog